00:14:28.610 --> 00:14:33.270
Underneath-- [LAUGHTER] it's
where I've seen some recently,

00:14:33.270 --> 00:14:34.270
which is a little scary.

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:39.780
Well, this view graph
says it hunts in open air.

00:14:39.780 --> 00:14:40.960
