00:49:19.120 --> 00:49:20.050
AUDIENCE: This one right here.

00:49:20.050 --> 00:49:20.633
PROFESSOR: OK.

00:49:20.633 --> 00:49:22.980
AUDIENCE: The last graph,
like the middle bottom.

00:49:22.980 --> 00:49:24.246
PROFESSOR: This guy?

00:49:24.246 --> 00:49:28.214
AUDIENCE: Why is that the
